# TypeScript incremental build cache. Per-machine artifact — when committed
# it tells `tsc` "everything is up to date" on whatever box pulls it,
# causing the compiler to skip emit and ship stale dist/. Real cause of
# the recurring "Property X does not exist on type AuditAction" errors
# during prod deploys.
*.tsbuildinfo
keys/*.pem
keys/*.key
**/keys/*.pem
**/keys/*.key
*.pem
*.key
